t = int(input())
for _ in range(t):
    line = input()
    words = line.split()
    nums = [int(w) for w in words]
    (p1, p2, k) = nums
    s = p1 + p2
    c = s // k
    if c % 2 == 0:
        print('CHEF')
    else:
        print('COOK')

for _ in range(int(input())):
    (a, b, c) = map(int, input().split())
    ans = (a + b) // c
    print('CHEF') if ans % 2 == 0 else print('COOK')

t = int(input())
for i in range(t):
    (a, b, k) = [int(i) for i in input().split()]
    print('CHEF') if (a + b) % (2 * k) < k else print('COOK')

for _ in range(int(input())):
    (P1, P2, K) = [i for i in map(int, input().split())]
    total_points = P1 + P2
    points = total_points // K
    players = ['CHEF', 'COOK']
    print(players[points % 2])
